      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T17:06:51+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Last night a lot happened in the world of sports! Tune in for my takes on @FirstTake",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034995056818450460",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-20T14:06:44+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Cade Cunningham, get better my brother!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034751921899155967",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T22:00:36+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "There\u2019s nobody better to break down the new WNBA CBA than @chiney. Insight, experience, and the real perspective the game deserves.\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034740342633750697",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T21:14:35+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "I said what I said!!! piped.video/Qn7u4el2cBo?si=wnrl\u2026",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034737964283052249",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T21:05:08+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The phone lines are open until 3PM, but this ain\u2019t for the unprepared.\n\nIf you\u2019re calling in, come with a real question and something to say.\n\nI\u2019m LIVE on The Stephen A. Smith Show.\n\n\ud83d\udcde (888-623-3646)\n\ud83c\udfa7 sxm.app.link/SASonSXM\n\nStep up. Deliver. Holla at your boy on @MadDogRadio!\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034691579378573809",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T18:00:49+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Everybody\u2019s got an opinion\u2026and my show is where you can share it! \n\nI\u2019m LIVE right now on The Stephen A. Smith Show.\nIf your take is really that strong, prove it by calling in between 1pm - 3pm!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034676430047477947",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T17:00:38+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "It\u2019s a new day to talk about all things sports! @FirstTake",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034624874732220790",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T13:35:46+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Big shout out to @HUMensBB for bringing home a WIN against UMBC! Way to represent for HBCUs!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034437632529236315",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T01:11:44+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Is the GOP in serious trouble?\npiped.video/hZEn785lM6A",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034433338161664287",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-19T00:54:40+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Rep. Kevin Kiley and I speak on all things politics! Join the conversation by calling in before 8PM and giving us your take! \n\n\u260e\ufe0f Call: 866-967-6887",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034411174754656423",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T23:26:36+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 TONIGHT: The country is moving FAST and I need YOUR voice on this:\n\n- The SAVE Act...\n- Oil prices going UP...\n\nAnd somehow we\u2019re supposed to believe everything is under control?!\n\nI don\u2019t think so.\n\n\ud83d\udcde CALL IN: 866-967-6887\n\nLet\u2019s talk about it LIVE on Straight Shooter @SIRIUSXM!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034389485429866650",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T22:00:25+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "We are in the SECOND HALF \u2026trust me, we are just getting warmed up! \n\nCALL THE SHOW: 888-623-3646\nLISTEN NOW: sxm.app.link/MadDogRadio",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034331930469212284",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T18:11:42+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "You know what time it is!!! Call in today from 1pm - 3pm EST!!! Don\u2019t sit on your take, SAY IT!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034315342986494361",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T17:05:48+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The SAVE Act is sparking major debate across the country!\nIs this about protecting election integrity\u2026 or restricting voter access? \n\nHere's a way to get your voice heard: Record or text your political take for my Straight Shooter Show every Wednesday at 6pm -8pm EST! bit.ly/4sSoDQ4\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034299073293946966",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T16:01:09+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Make sure you tune this morning! We are LIVE!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034286252443197482",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T15:10:12+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Oil prices rising. Flights delayed. Markets shaky.\u2028How much of this war is about energy control?",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034277436825727392",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T14:35:10+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Did the U.S. enter this war on its own terms or because of allies?",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034276808774852694",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T14:32:40+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
